
Welcome to Xen Orchestra community edition VM based on https://github.com/ronivay/XenOrchestraInstallerUpdater

This is not official Xen Orchestra appliance and comes with no support. Report any issues to github page above.

XenOrchestraInstallerUpdater is installed under /opt and can be used to update existing Xen Orchestra installation. Installations at /opt/xo

self-signed ssl certificate are at /opt/ssl. You may replace these with your own if you wish.

Xen Orchestra runs as a xo-server systemd service. 

xo user has full sudo access. Xen Orchestra updates and service control should be run with sudo.


